meters, meters, kilometers, inches, feet, yards, and miles. This flexibilit=
y makes it suitable for both academic use and professional applications in =
engineering, architecture, and construction.</p><hr data-start=3D"1854" dat=
a-end=3D"1857"><h3 data-start=3D"1859" data-end=3D"1899">3. Why Use a Perim=
