ata-end=3D"3322">Perimeter Calculator</strong> allows you to input the radi=
us and instantly get the circumference.</p><h4 data-start=3D"3394" data-end=
=3D"3418">4.5 Parallelogram</h4><p data-start=3D"3419" data-end=3D"3554">Th=
